        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Trichocline cisplatina. A. Habit (E. Pasini et al. 897, ICN). Black arrows indicates the position of the secundary lobes of the leaves. B. Representative capitulum (E. Pasini et al. 898, ICN). C. Outermost to innermost phyllaries (E. Pasini et al. 898, ICN). D. Pistillate ray floret (Cabrera 32122, SI). E. Bisexual disc floret (Cabrera 32122, SI). F. Stamen of bisexual disc floret (Cabrera 32122, SI). G. Staminode of pistillate ray florets (Cabrera 32122, SI). H. Ovary (Cabrera 32122, SI). I. Trichome of the ovary (E. Pasini et al. 897, ICN). Illustration by João Vieira Iganci." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894806/files/figure.png" .

